nodes.text: The SoroSuub skyhook was located above Coruscant.

The skyhook was offered to the former members of Rogue Squadron after they resigned their commissions from the New Republic to liberate Thyferra from Ysanne Isard. However, the New Republic Provisional Council issued an order to ground all skyhooks near the area where the Lusankya was buried in order to provide housing for the survivors.
